---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact — KKT"
  description="Book a diagnostic with KKT. Tallinn, EU."
  ogImage="/og/contact.png"
>
  <article class="prose-page">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="section-label">Contact</div>
      <h1 class="h1-page">Book a diagnostic.</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        Tell us what your business is trying to move — margin, cash,
        availability, customer value, or productivity — and we will tell you
        whether AI and PMO discipline can earn their place in it.
      </p>

      <div class="contact-block">
        <div class="contact-row">
          <div class="contact-label">Email</div>
          <a href="mailto:hello@kittykat.tech">hello@kittykat.tech</a>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-row">
          <div class="contact-label">Phone</div>
          <a href="tel:+37255553621">+372 5555 3621</a>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-row">
          <div class="contact-label">Office</div>
          <div>Jõe 7, 10151 Tallinn, Estonia</div>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-row">
          <div class="contact-label">LinkedIn</div>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/kittykattech/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">linkedin.com/company/kittykattech</a>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-row">
          <div class="contact-label">Legal</div>
          <div>Kitty Kat Technologies OÜ</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="next-steps">
        <div class="section-label">What happens next</div>
        <h2 class="next-h2">After you email.</h2>
        <ol class="steps">
          <li>
            <div class="step-num">01</div>
            <div>
              <div class="step-name">Reply within two working days.</div>
              <p>One of us reads your note and writes back. No SDR
              chain, no scheduling forms.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="step-num">02</div>
            <div>
              <div class="step-name">A 30-minute call.</div>
              <p>Senior person on our side. We hear the situation
              honestly and tell you whether a diagnostic makes
              sense — or whether the answer is "not us".</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="step-num">03</div>
            <div>
              <div class="step-name">If a fit, scope a diagnostic.</div>
              <p>Two weeks, fixed shape, decision-grade readout. See
              <a href="/approach">/approach</a> for the day-by-day.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <blockquote class="contact-pull">
        <p>
          If a diagnostic is not the right move, we will say so on the
          first call. No mystery sales motion.
        </p>
      </blockquote>

      <p class="note">
        Not sure if you&rsquo;re a fit?
        <a href="/not-for-you">Read /not-for-you</a> first — that
        page filters faster than a sales call.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose-page {
    padding-top: clamp(40px, 6vh, 72px);
    padding-bottom: clamp(56px, 9vh, 96px);
  }
  .narrow { max-width: 760px; }
  .section-label { margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .h1-page {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4.5vw, 48px);
    line-height: 1.16;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .lede {
    font-size: clamp(17px, 2vw, 20px);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.55;
    max-width: 56ch;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  .contact-block {
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-top: 24px;
  }
  .contact-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr;
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  .contact-label {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 600;
    align-self: center;
  }
  .contact-row a { color: var(--text-primary); }
  .next-steps {
    margin-top: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    padding-top: 36px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .next-steps .section-label { margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .next-h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3.4vw, 32px);
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  .steps {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 14px;
    max-width: 720px;
  }
  .steps li {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 56px 1fr;
    gap: 18px;
    padding: 20px 22px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--accent-text);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .step-name {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    font-size: 16px;
  }
  .steps p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; max-width: 56ch; }
  .steps a { color: var(--text-primary); }

  .contact-pull {
    margin: 32px 0;
    padding: 22px 26px;
    background: var(--surface-alt);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
    max-width: 720px;
  }
  .contact-pull p {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2.4vw, 22px);
    line-height: 1.35;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 36ch;
  }

  .note {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 56ch;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }
  .note a { color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 500; }
</style>
